casebody.data:
Wednesday, November 22, 1995

MERIT DOCKET

95-1941. State ex rel. Kilpatrick v. Ingraham.

In Prohibition. On amended complaint and motion for stay. Sua sponte, leave to file the amended complaint is granted, and the amended complaint is dismissed. Motion for stay denied.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
